    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.26b.16-17_0001"/>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">16</fw>
                
                <opener>
                    <dateline>July 17, 1958</dateline>
                
                    <salute>Dear John,</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>Congratulations on your new <hi rend="caps">TV</hi> show. The folks sent me a clipping about your class which will be taught over <hi rend="caps">KOMU-TV</hi>. I think it is wonderful. Good luck with this new venture.</p>
                
                <p>How is Alice's new training farm coming along? Did they go through with their plans? Say "Hello" to everyone for me.</p>
                
                <p>I will see you in August and we will record as many tapes as we can. I want to release one this Fall and two more in the Spring, if we can do that many tapes.</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>Affectionate thoughts,</salute>
                
                    <signed>Sandy</signed>
                </closer>
                
            </div1>
            
            
